What is that smell?

00:20:49.374 --> 00:20:52.127 position:50% align:center
Never mind. You've had your fun.
Put that away!

00:20:52.210 --> 00:20:54.462 position:50% align:center
Aw! But I just started!

00:20:54.546 --> 00:20:56.381 position:50% align:center
[AMOS] Don't look at me.
I didn't give the order.

00:20:56.464 --> 00:20:58.174 position:50% align:center
Just do as you're told.

00:20:58.258 --> 00:21:01.720 position:50% align:center
This comes from the head of
the City Guard, Tesla, himself!

00:21:01.803 --> 00:21:05.598 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA] Dang it!
I didn't have any fun at all!

00:21:05.682 --> 00:21:08.476 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Hm? What's it say?

00:21:08.560 --> 00:21:14.649 position:50% align:center
"Nice Shower Best Friend Killer:
Amicide Who Had an 'Accident.'"

00:21:14.733 --> 00:21:17.610 position:50% align:center
Awkwardly worded, but accurate.

00:21:17.694 --> 00:21:20.238 position:50% align:center
You know, I don't think you
realize it, but you've managed

00:21:20.321 --> 00:21:21.906 position:50% align:center
to do something incredible.

00:21:21.990 --> 00:21:23.825 position:50% align:center
Y-You've discovered
a new cheat!

00:21:23.908 --> 00:21:25.952 position:50% align:center
Quit treating it
like a workaround!

00:21:26.036 --> 00:21:27.871 position:50% align:center
But it's an entirely
unknown strategy!

00:21:27.954 --> 00:21:29.789 position:50% align:center
No one's ever thought
of it before!

00:21:29.873 --> 00:21:31.541 position:50% align:center
You're the first player
in the game's history

00:21:31.624 --> 00:21:34.502 position:50% align:center
who soiled himself
to evade torture!

00:21:34.586 --> 00:21:38.590 position:50% align:center
[AMOS grunts]
Ugh. Get up already.

00:21:38.673 --> 00:21:40.759 position:50% align:center
[HIRO grunting]

00:21:44.346 --> 00:21:45.638 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Wait! What are you doing?

00:21:45.722 --> 00:21:48.266 position:50% align:center
You can't log out now!

00:21:48.350 --> 00:21:52.562 position:50% align:center
You've made serious progress!
It's about to get super fun!

00:21:52.645 --> 00:21:54.898 position:50% align:center
You call this fun?

00:21:54.981 --> 00:21:56.149 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:21:56.232 --> 00:22:01.905 position:50% align:center
This is not fun!
It's complete and utter garbage!

00:22:01.988 --> 00:22:03.490 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:22:03.573 --> 00:22:06.409 position:50% align:center
Screw this game!
And screw all of you!

00:22:06.493 --> 00:22:08.995 position:50% align:center
I am done!

00:23:46.051 --> 00:23:49.471 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Episode 4:
"The Only One to Beat the Game."